https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F23%2F214000_dd51e1d4848b38a1b7ac928273a0f856.gif&h=d8915994&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">曹婦與狗不得內進（狗？就係講緊你啊油飯）</div></span></span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\"><strong>入黎討論前 請先睇曹柔里既十七宗罪<br />\n注：如果唔想受到極大驚嚇建議唔好開自動LOAD圖，你可以選擇逐張㩒以一個循序漸進嘅方式去提高自己嘅接受能力</strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">老鼠屎曹柔里</span></strong><br />\nIdol School 時期：<br />\n一、偶校時期出曬名靠扮有情上位<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/09/03/LH0K2f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F09%2F03%2FLH0K2f.png&h=0453d0bd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n二、評價舞台環節 &nbsp;見到有組員0票 大家都被隊友既零分嚇到的時候 佢自己微微的笑左一下 咁岩就比鏡頭影到 反應如下<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/15/183734_c5ee0ef1b3d3c76b614b20da3f6f6220.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F15%2F183734_c5ee0ef1b3d3c76b614b20da3f6f6220.gif&h=b8bbc6b8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\npd48 時期：<br />\n三、個人評價唱唱下停係度 仲好淡定 PD史上第一次有人由A跌到F 當然會多啲鏡頭<br />\n四、參加日韓合作節目 開頭仲扮到好nice咁話會幫朱里 但練習時帶住<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>慰安婦徽章</strong></span><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/29/000624_79924e6172164ef70f197aa7ff5ab0ee.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F29%2F000624_79924e6172164ef70f197aa7ff5ab0ee.gif&h=80521caf&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/29/000632_7e53c70ccb91bbf76093704c1d393aec.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F29%2F000632_7e53c70ccb91bbf76093704c1d393aec.gif&h=ddc9a402&s={SIZE}\" />完全唔尊重日本妹 前期節目花絮入面無見過佢同日本妹交流 就後期淨係識痴住話題性高既nako<br />\n五、Position評價明明唱得無羅高恩好 都要爭Main Vocal 最後要成組降key就佢 仲要羅高恩教返佢點唱<br />\n六、第二次排名公佈 喊到要喊出聲先有人知佢喊緊 但一滴眼淚都無 虛偽<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/03/210754_24793cdc7720db9b1be5d22d83b1fe86.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F03%2F210754_24793cdc7720db9b1be5d22d83b1fe86.gif&h=53022010&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n七、Concept評價開頭話想換歌 但之後踢人走又跪哂地話想留低唔唱main vocal都得 留低之後又搶過<br />\n八、傾踢邊個走期間無啦啦唱1000% 同公司狗竹都忍唔住串佢話歌詞都背好 暗指某婦係咪準備好過去<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/12/121629_c1ce6e370315255c0d912f21f5c810db.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F12%2F121629_c1ce6e370315255c0d912f21f5c810db.png&h=c872d405&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/12/121629_97f9fe0134cde845098fd839fd6d51c8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F12%2F121629_97f9fe0134cde845098fd839fd6d51c8.png&h=123dd895&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n九、最後排名公佈 上次18名升到第3名 扮驚訝 扮感動 但一滴眼淚都無 睇下同樣情況既安有真 金珉周同金彩元 反應差天共地 有d腦既都會睇得出<br />\n以下係某婦同AJY嘅完美配合<br />\n十、Final揀位 瘋狂比人踢走 大大聲講無野話唔緊要 下一個shot即刻播海允比人踢完喊 成功營造天使image<br />\n十一、Final首歌降key唱 soyou仲要讚佢 明明降key其他人都唱到 AJY捧佢捧到出哂面<br />\n偶校已經對佢好反感 但今次pd48見佢實力改善咗嘗試接受佢 但佢啲行為愈黎愈虛偽<br />\n十二、Vlive 唔出聲無人理 唯一一次仲要係佢自己叫Sad Frog餵 <br />\n十三、自九月一日起日日都有新面孔<br />\n十四、Nekkoya 練習片一個第三名嘅Vocal係Dance Break企C 仲要跳錯 <br />\n十五、八婆撞我元英 Dance Break完就以為自己係C,唔係見到禾櫻轉去C位跳都唔知自己跳錯<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/icCnwNA.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FicCnwNA.gif&h=0f73af50&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n十六、唔知佢想點,hi醬生日v 成堆人攬埋一夠得佢企左邊<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ONS6Zs2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FONS6Zs2.png&h=53afd6e8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/O4RDjeG.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FO4RDjeG.gif&h=a939c476&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n十七、hi醬生日v 佢拎牙咬嘢仲要周圍吐,仲要一野撞走禾真,嗰粒嘢嚇到禾真之外,佢仲lur咗落啲匙羹到 btw佢推個膊頭出黎嗰下好似楊怡gif<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"https://wemedia01-prod.s3-ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/media/images/318355/org/66ee49c04cf4832044caedf9b327a36f.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwemedia01-prod.s3-ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F318355%2Forg%2F66ee49c04cf4832044caedf9b327a36f.gif&h=cfa8029c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/wh62NDl.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fwh62NDl.gif&h=27dccfa3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nby資深偶校飯 丁丁車<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: pink;\">本討論區是韓國Mnet在2018年推出的選拔實境節目《Produce 48》撚鳩參加者同觀眾後，而推出的屌柒區</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/10/151823_79dc4aa3b328f0c499b67adf13e2f339.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F10%2F151823_79dc4aa3b328f0c499b67adf13e2f339.png&h=e6d37a73&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\"><strong>食屎啦mnet</strong></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/10/151847_538b7f48334279f57f48b5d36944bb0d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F10%2F151847_538b7f48334279f57f48b5d36944bb0d.png&h=6460dd88&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">除了曺柔理外，所有曾參與《Produce 48》的參加者皆可在此討論</span></span><br />\nIONE有份代言嘅遊戲Overhit攻略<br />\n<a href=\"http://overhit.game100.wiki/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Foverhit.game100.wiki%2F&d=pVqiA2KGJfIis%2Bm8MYXWdY9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=8d204c44\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://overhit.game100