" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n11.禾櫻細個發脾四<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.weibo.cn/status/4293232986982877?#&amp;video\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.weibo.cn%2Fstatus%2F4293232986982877%3F%23%26video&d=pVqiA2KGJfIis%2Bm8MYXWdY9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=cac69c02\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.weibo.cn/status/4293232986982877?#&amp;video</a><br />\n<br />\n12.彩元181006球埸hd<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/fwvmwaX\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/fwvmwaX</a><br />\n<br />\n13.阿裴去咗mru ig live留言<br />\n唔識日文淨係打genki genki<br />\n打極都係韓文<br />\nMiru講左句:韓文啊...分からない<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/cLz6C_c8-HU?t=1351\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FcLz6C_c8-HU%3Ft%3D1351&d=pVqiA2KGJfIis%2Bm8MYXWdY9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=60b5aec1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/cLz6C_c8-HU?t=1351</a><br />\n<br />\n14.日本妹壯行會<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/09/231225_f4a4a0e9bb23b3c0c109dcbb5b8c2035.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F09%2F231225_f4a4a0e9bb23b3c0c109dcbb5b8c2035.png&h=267d0f5b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n15.<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/NDc8YTq.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FNDc8YTq.gif&h=c3e30fdb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/2itWD5y.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F2itWD5y.gif&h=062ae4bf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n16.簽售會討論<br />\n#817,819,822,824-26,831,834,841,844,852,853,858,859,860-61,911-13<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n17.what is high touch<br />\n#870,#875<br />\n<br />\n18.<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/10/003630_69f14473ef0570cf2547df98d7506f39.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F10%2F003630_69f14473ef0570cf2547df98d7506f39.gif&h=a9218dc0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n19.<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n20.https://youtu.be/uaBOUCGf5Wk<br />\n好似係肥妹以前啦啦隊比賽"},{"pid":"26dff391a3072bdfb0462bc7275cc09bb53294d7","tid":855142,"uid":204923,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T01:05:59.000Z","msg":"21.如果你純買碟的話<br />\n學各位巴絲話齋去Gmarket買好過<br />\n假設裴巴要買10隻fromis 9<br />\n瘋狂抽佢竹佢淵兼衝銷量<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/10/075319_264535584b8bbfbe6e463476455a2d09.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F10%2F075319_264535584b8bbfbe6e463476455a2d09.png&h=88e6a855&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n一隻碟八十幾（未計國內同國際運費）<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/10/075411_725cd5f2623d521f330fc96f11553b7e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F10%2F075411_725cd5f2623d521f330fc96f11553b7e.png&h=6b4b7047&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n記得喺呢度買先啱，因為計銷售量<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/10/075510_16bbed973dcc4acf5305ad2c36a62bb7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F10%2F075510_16bbed973dcc4acf5305ad2c36a62bb7.png&h=fea25e71&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nSynnara平日有兩種國內運費，一款係2500won，買幾多隻碟都係2500，一種係免運費，但隻碟售價會貴啲，分分鐘貴過2500，所以個人買開運費2500嗰種<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/10/075822_98e04fdcff850bff62042cda75f525b2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F10%2F075822_98e04fdcff850bff62042cda75f525b2.png&h=f3132750&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n國際運輸最抵一定係sf，長期做優惠之餘梗有一間喺左近，ems一無人收貨就要去郵局抬番去，cj我玩過一次，速度慢之餘又難check個track，不了<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/10/080058_7a6a5cea05a71ef0c645c042c295e1ce.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F10%2F080058_7a6a5cea05a71ef0c645c042c295e1ce.png&h=2413d53d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n送到你屋企平均每隻都唔洗100，你仲可以加7蚊港紙買海報（f9呢隻碟無得揀加海報），你出去買都要過百蚊仲蝕埋車錢都唔抵啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nSynnara唯一嘅唔好處就係唔洗碟&nbsp;&nbsp;<br />\n好大機會十幾隻連number 咁入面小卡就一樣<br />\n不過依家少咗十幾隻連住<br />\n通常都係三四隻連<br />\n<br />\n至於mnet簽名碟<br />\n其實就係去呢個網買碟<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mwave.me/en/kpop-store/cd?ctgr=9001\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mwave.me%2Fen%2Fkpop-store%2Fcd%3Fctgr%3D9001&d=pVqiA2KGJfIis%2Bm8MYXWdY9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=44c21490\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mwave.me/en/kpop-store/cd?ctgr=9001</a><br />\n時不時會賣signed album <br />\n近排係weki meki got7 宇宙少女 pentagon <br />\n不過就有排等<br />\n特別係個星好忙嘅<br />\n隻碟出咗3個月之後先收到貨都唔奇<br />\n有時整簽名碟嘅目的係要搞一個名為meet and greet嘅網上直播節目<br />\n買得最多嗰幾個就會讀吓你個名同留言<br />\n同有啲額外禮物送<br />\n不外乎自拍即影即有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢啲時候有好多妹妹仔喺ig開團谷上榜咁<br />\n都係嗰句啦ig涉及風險<br />\n避得就避<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n22.斬妹準備找數<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/10/084742_10a1c4ebd095df21b65e05fe330c3139.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F10%2F084742_10a1c4ebd095df21b65e05fe330c3139.png&h=d9b4c114&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0f6b063b9c032db738b925d273093ad58779a15f","tid":855142,"uid":204923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T01:06:51.000Z","msg":"唔記得開喺韓國台<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"240a336ad152abbe5412bd71067d0bcec19a80e8","tid":855142,"uid":174221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T01:07:10.000Z","msg":"咩標題黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkg